Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  終於到了喚醒那位大人的時候了
Comment: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:22.70,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯、資料：電車の神；校對：遠ぃ風；\N特效：Noeru、sollun；時間：nagiau；後期：wyitalia、zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜脈認證  確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,視網膜認證  確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Children{\i} 她們是好孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局長  那位大人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們B.A.B.E.L的創立有關的重大功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經睡了差不多有十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  十年？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以該說是很難對付還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「詛咒所有妨礙我睡眠的人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便叫醒她的話似乎會大吵大鬧的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這次沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也聽到她的聲音了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  眼鏡君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是桐壺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前幾天真是太感謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據前任局長的指示  只要少佐一有行動就要來叫醒您…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}上次累死我了  現在還沒睡飽  你下個月再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…呃…就算您這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有叫醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…裡面的這位大人和兵部有什麼關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關係可大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是那傢伙的前同僚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同僚？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說超過80歲了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對兵部少佐的拘束和監禁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有她的力量是不可能辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了抑制住P.A.N.D.R.A就必須儘快將她叫醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吵了  會讓人睡不著的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看…看來心情很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天還是先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告  警告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有入侵者  有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說過不能來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…想見你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生是我的Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐  皆本你也很想見到我們的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事怎樣都無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  怎樣都無所謂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  這是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  發現好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是來和我幽會的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳…妳在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳真的有80歲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要提年齡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了  皆本先生被女人襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  你在做什麼啊  皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何…何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您醒了嗎  蕾見不二子管理官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼馬上去本部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前要先吃早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管理官？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是年輕人啊  被吸了這麼多還這麼有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  因為這女人的性騷擾  什麼東西變得有精神了啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦  妳們好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚妳們的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這位小弟的這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都還只過是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險  直美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了妳我願意死無數次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會因為這點程度就死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  事情大條了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎  薰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  完全沒有打中的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是LV7的念動能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  薰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們友好相處吧  明石薰妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  接觸感應能力？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢…慢著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓妳久等了～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有等  我完全沒在等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  美味的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的初吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且對方據說還是80歲的老奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫁不出去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  對不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太小題大作了  這只是打招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過碰觸而吸取能量的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就某種意義上來說比兵部少佐還難對付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為同伴還真是亦喜亦悲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡眠期間的報告書就這麼多了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超能力者和普通人的對立升高嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不二子  要開始忙碌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果需要更詳細的資料的話  請儘管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我有馬上想知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我妳們使用的化妝品～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過了10年  化妝技術也進化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種睫毛膏加了珍珠粉  會讓睫毛光華柔順哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是增強眼神力度的睫毛膏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這顏色很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再一起聊女生話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到現在還是憧憬著不可觸及的過去和未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的老化停止現象是吸取能量這種能力的副作用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這能力本來的作用是透過吸取的能量來提升自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這能力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和{\i1}The Children{\i} 一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管…管理官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要條件具備的話  就能達到LV7的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是瞬間最大風速這種東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提  你能叫我不二子妹妹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者至少叫我蕾見小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太…太強人所難了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  還有一件事～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能當成是被狗咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被狗咬了會忘記嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵妳太少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是個吻罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻想太美好的話  真正要做的時候可就麻煩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了  見多了男女感情事的接觸感應能力者的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫穗  妳真的是第一次嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  要好好注意那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不能毫不還手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且皆本啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要儘早調教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說啊  你不要再負責{\i1}The Children{\i} 了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不二子正式命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這是什麼命令啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有理由就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有理由哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照現在這樣下去  {\i1}The Children{\i} 最終會變成兵部所期望的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵部所期望的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是辦不到的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有改變命運的力量和覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午是○○  到外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午後は○○。外で遊ぼう！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潤滑唇膏  呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,うるうるリップ。きゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有改變命運的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不曉得  不二子也不是很清楚～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟知道多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  現在就進行部署轉換
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  請…請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公務員是不能頂撞命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BYE-BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  接下來情況會怎麼變化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠻橫的人事變動！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人事調動？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  研究開發部突然急需他的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫穗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這違反服務規定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個老奶奶指使的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力也是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是局長重視的盆栽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐嚇更加不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不可能接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  皆本先生和我們約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會一直和我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是管理官好像有什麼想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過一陣子我一定會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過一陣子是什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之現在要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實預知課發來了出擊的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來後一定要把這個問題解決啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和新主任好好執行任務哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新主任？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到今早的共同練習的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠如此之快地發揮作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美 & {\i1}The Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解禁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,純淨正確狂野地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對有些無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  感覺很失望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來在位居高位的人手中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀麗純潔{\i1}Wild Cat{\i}  and…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為漏油而導致的油輪大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離事故發生還有30分鐘以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要冷靜處理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得異常的安靜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  沒有人的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪  也沒有漏油的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…什麼陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等妳們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本  為什麼在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  皆本？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是醫生嘛  會定期到研究所來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  沒想到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  賢木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有不是B.A.B.E.L配屬的手機嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您撥打的號碼被限制通話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據國家機密防治法  此電話會自動銷毀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  這個也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你要怎麼負責啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有女孩子的郵寄地址啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法和{\i1}Children{\i} 取得聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是管理官的所為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管理官？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是想將我們徹底分離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這讓我怎麼能接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和那些孩子都不是國家的所有物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本  雖然我不清楚詳細情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之你被監視了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反抗上司的話  不只是開除就能了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕  監禁  該不會連射殺的許可都有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  反正有工資拿的  就乖一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我  皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個影像…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的幻想或妄想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  她們有那麼強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳送來心電感應也不是什麼不可思議的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如果現在不去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢木  幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我  直美  {\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  火…火災發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝進去的那些孩子沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美  {\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  為什麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為妳們會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙  果然是敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要打嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要露出這麼可怕的表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為妳們著想才這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在睜眼說瞎話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼作為我是你們同伴的證據  我告訴你們一件非常重大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本君  現在正在朝這邊趕來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  照我說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話  我就把他給幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使違背命令也要來救妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他因為擔心妳們胸口都快要撕裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  不覺得有一個問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他來說{\i1}Children{\i} 只是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像妹妹一樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  再過幾年可能就會察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些孩子也是美妙的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這樣就太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上帶妳們去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…就這樣抱著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像戀人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  就算只有現在這點時間也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是只有現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迄今為止都是  今後也一直是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在快要失去的時候  才第一次意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將妳作為一名女性去愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…等一下  剛才的展開不覺得太勉強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直美～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的直美～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在快要失去妳的時候我意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將妳作為一名女性愛著…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是例外  例外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣  絕對會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾見管理官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然違背我不二子的命令來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就清楚地告訴我你的心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和{\i1}Children{\i} 不是只透過工作相連的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在需要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以改變命運的   強大的愛的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能因為一個命令就和她們分開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算很微小  只要有種子的話我就會將它培育起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  問題在於那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差點真實性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳…妳們！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:20:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  小孩真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本  檢查的結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Children{\i} …連擦傷都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大團圓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果就是說大家一起在耍我嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我只是遵從命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本  不要這麼生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生也有不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  整天都說我們小孩子小孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我願意原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就當作是彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  所以這件事就到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在執行重要任務的時候妳們都在做些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  還半開玩笑地玩弄我擔心妳們的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們把我…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這工作當成什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做這種事情的話  就去找其他負責人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  皆本…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我  我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種工作我不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生  我明白你的感受…冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會和管理官好好談談的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本
Comment: 0,0:22:10.46,0:23:39.25,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,『Break+Your+Destiny』作詞：六見純代\N作曲：渡邊珊\N編曲：增田武史\N唄：遊佐浩二&中村悠一&谷山紀章
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:26.24,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,緊緊地抱住逞強的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:29.21,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,就連難過的側臉　全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:31.55,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,讓·人·喜·愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:35.76,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,每次突破障礙都會變強的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:41.68,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼·睛　沒有不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.93,0:22:46.95,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,過於率直的內心情感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:50.48,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,是不會輸給任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:55.74,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會放開妳　不管在什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:23:00.95,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,這看不到結局的一切　由我來改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:05.30,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是惡魔和天使都有著翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:10.93,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,指引前往更高的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:15.63,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,不會再讓妳的笑容變得陰沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.63,0:23:22.04,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,連結的希望　現在撕裂了黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:24.97,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,和妳一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:30.93,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}向著明天飛躍　Break Your Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i} 是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這片海是伊號喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊號喜歡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果伊號沒事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.41,0:23:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  就能證明那樣悲慘的未來並不是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您全都知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第29話  「花言巧語！離天國最近的大海」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面  我是未摘花江
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼能馬上將這孩子洗腦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐  所以不會輸！
